{
  "3132930": {
    "name": "纪念碑谷 3",
    "steam_appid": 3132930,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132930/extras/6b793a7fb1fd4bd0a2774121bcaefb75.avif?t=1765537431\" width=653 height=191 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>延续经典</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由备受赞誉的独立游戏工作室ustwo games研发，团队代表作不仅包括获奖无数的《纪念碑谷》系列，还有广受好评的《Land’s End》、《Assemble with Care》以及《Alba: A Wildlife Adventure》。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《纪念碑谷 3》不仅延续了此前系列作品的精美视觉艺术风格和解谜玩法，还在鬼斧神工的几何结构设计之上，带你走出纪念碑，走向宽阔的大海。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132930/extras/60a004bae30a333eb0908f81819bc184.poster.avif?t=1765537431\" width=620 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132930/extras/60a004bae30a333eb0908f81819bc184.webm?t=1765537431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>开启奇妙航程</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扬帆起航吧，Noor！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >去到变幻的建筑中，去到翻涌的潮汐间，去探寻你的勇气与智慧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >世界的光芒正在逐渐消退，去寻找重燃神圣之光的秘法，如若不然，你所珍视的家园将被无穷无尽的海浪，吞没殆尽。拯救是为了探索自己，从不只是为了成为英雄。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132930/extras/78c166b7770a011f3329276f5d03f91c.poster.avif?t=1765537431\" width=620 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132930/extras/78c166b7770a011f3329276f5d03f91c.webm?t=1765537431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>破与立</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重力的法则将被打破？还是重力本身只是我们思维的定式……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >逻辑和直觉将是你奇幻航行中最好的辅助工具，但也记得打开想象力的窗户，灵光乍现时，转换个思路又或者是变换个角度。那些曾经困扰你的迷雾或执惘，都将不复存在。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132930/extras/steamstorevideo_cutscenemontage_wide.gif?t=1765537431\" /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>更多体验敬请期待</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《纪念碑谷 3》登陆Steam首发即包含完整剧情。后续我们还将持续推出更多全新解谜关卡与故事章节。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132930/extras/d3dadd2d0426d4d224a8c634aabc5738.poster.avif?t=1765537431\" width=620 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132930/extras/d3dadd2d0426d4d224a8c634aabc5738.webm?t=1765537431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏核心特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•在惊艳绝伦的场景中解开颠覆认知的立体谜题</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•探索由视错觉与空间透视构筑的全新场景</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•在不可能的几何结构与圣光中体验丰富动人的情感旅程</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•包含所有未来更新内容，无需额外付费</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 日语, 韩语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 瑞典语, 繁体中文, 土耳其语, 丹麦语, 荷兰语, 俄语, 简体中文, 乌克兰语, 越南语, 菲律宾语, 马来语",
